data.description: $10,000 price improvement!! PLUS Seller paid $2,500 towards buyers closing cost & 1 YEAR HOME WARRANTY with accepted offer that closes on or before January 31, 2024!! Beautiful Blake Taylor built home in the coveted Crestwood subdivision. This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home boasts gorgeous hardwood floors along with a split floor plan for added privacy. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and custom cabinets. This home has a large master with a walk-in closet and the master bath has granite countertops, double vanity, large soaking tub and walk-in tiled shower. The backyard offers ample privacy and is fully fenced. There's also a screened in back porch which is great for entertaining. Come see this home before it's gone!
